<item>
            <title>[HBASE-885] TableMap and TableReduce should be interfaces</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-885</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;TableMap and TableReduce are abstract classes which makes it impossible to write a class that maps from and reduce to hbase. IMHO, they should be interfaces since they only define a single and static method.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
